high_descs: Go forward a bit, turn left, go to the fridge, turn right, go to the end of the counter, turn left
Pick up the mug in the coffee maker
Turn left, go to the fridge, turn right
Open the fridge, put the cup in the fridge, close the fridge, wait, open the fridge, pick the cup, close the fridge
Turn right, go to the coffee maker, turn left
Put the cup into the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Cool a mug in the fridge

high_descs: Turn left, hang a right at the fridge, and head towards the coffee maker sitting on the counter to your left.
Pick up the white mug on the coffee maker.
Turn to your left and head to the fridge that will be on your right.
Place the coffee mug in the fridge to chill before taking it back out.
Turn to your right and head back to the coffee maker.
Place the mug to where it is located under the coffee maker's spout.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug under the coffee maker spout.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the fridge, then turn right and go to the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the cup on the shelf for a little bit and take it out.
Turn right and go back to the coffee machine.
Set the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Chill the mug and put it in the coffee machine.
